"6  small potatoes (1 1/2 pounds)","2 tablespoons reduced-fat sour cream","1/4 teaspoon kosher salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","2  scallions, sliced (white and green parts separated)","2 ounces sliced deli ham, chopped","1/2 cup grated sharp cheddar cheese"